OUR STORY
ABOUT US
It All Started In Dunedin- 1985
Eddie Turner started his little bar and grill in a narrow sliver of a building across from the Gulf of Mexico.  He succeeded because he made everyone feel welcome, and he gave his patrons great food and service.  Since then, thanks to the great people of Dunedin, the establishment has grown and evolved into something truly unique.
With new ownership in 2016 and an amazing remodel Eddie’s is now known as one of the best sports bars in Tampa Bay, Eddie’s Bar & Grill continues to deliver on Eddie’s original values! We have some of the best burgers in the country, award winning wings, and a sophisticated ever-changing selection of craft beers, wines there is something for everyone.
The gator mascot has also changed with the times, but he is still a symbol representing seriously good delivery with a touch of neighborly good humor.
We continue to add more locations across the Bay Area to serve you.  Eddie’s takes pride in offering you all your favorite sports, great food and drinks, in action packed atmosphere, with an amazing game area that will be fun for the whole family.
